Bhai tension mat le â€” **Deployment file yaad rakhna mushkil hota hi hai**, par main tujhe ek *formula-style spoon-feeding method* sikha deta hoon.

Agar tu yeh **5-step structure** yaad kar lega na,
toh Deployment YAML kabhi bhoolega hi nahi.

